# 🧠 BACKEND REQUIREMENTS

## Endpoint

### GET /api/ordenes

### Query Params

```id="query-params"
?fechaInicio=
&fechaFin=
&cliente=
&estado=
&page=
&limit=
```

---

## Responsibilities

* Fetch orders from WooCommerce
* Apply filters
* Paginate results
* Return simplified response

---

